<Link id="l00296" /><CodeLine lineNumber="296"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// If conveniently available, return the content of the given Section.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00297" /><CodeLine lineNumber="297"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  ///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00298" /><CodeLine lineNumber="298"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// When the section is available in the local address space, in relocated</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00299" /><CodeLine lineNumber="299"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// (loaded) form, e.g. because it was relocated by a JIT for execution, this</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00300" /><CodeLine lineNumber="300"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// function should provide the contents of said section in &#96;Data&#96;. If the</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00301" /><CodeLine lineNumber="301"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// loaded section is not available, or the cost of retrieving it would be</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00302" /><CodeLine lineNumber="302"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// prohibitive, this function should return false. In that case, relocations</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00303" /><CodeLine lineNumber="303"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// will be read from the local (unrelocated) object file and applied on the</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00304" /><CodeLine lineNumber="304"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// fly. Note that this method is used purely for optimzation purposes in the</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00305" /><CodeLine lineNumber="305"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// common case of JITting in the local address space, so returning false</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00306" /><CodeLine lineNumber="306"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// should always be correct.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00307" /><CodeLine lineNumber="307" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/llvm/loadedobjectinfo/#a8dc6570052d2945a88abb4d73b81c11a"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">virtual</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">bool</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/loadedobjectinfo/#a8dc6570052d2945a88abb4d73b81c11a">getLoadedSectionContents</a>(</span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">const</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/object/sectionref">object::SectionRef</a> &amp;Sec,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00308" /><CodeLine lineNumber="308"><span class="doxyHighlight">                                        <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/stringref">StringRef</a> &amp;<a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#aa20539e89704d20b98b97e9c3feac934">Data</a>)</span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword"> const </span><span class="doxyHighlight">&#123;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00309" /><CodeLine lineNumber="309"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">return</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">false</span><span class="doxyHighlight">;</span></CodeLine>
